{"tid":1394741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭心靈雞湯] 留意到勇武義士開始有負面情緒","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:41:22.000Z","uid":63452,"like":232,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"0b92d4e7063dfd702822fa834803e359d081a2a1","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有好多人因為各種原因上唔到最前線 </span>(體能，心理質素etc.，例如銀髮族)<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔代表佢地唔care/無付出</span>，大家一路有錢出錢有力出力，文筆好就做文宣<br />\n今次如果唔係文宣組咁落力，只係靠兩登自己圍爐，都唔會動員到咁多人<br />\n<br />\n我知最前線嘅人難免會同後排嘅人比，再同無出黎嘅人比，覺得點解我要比其他人付出多啲<br />\n但係其實<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都用自己嘅方法努力緊</span><br />\n屌後面嘅人只會孤立自己，令勇武嘅動員力更低<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n大家要互相體諒，明白大家嘅難處，不分化不割席，贏面先至會最大</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6d365be7a61b63ad87311a42759f17bc4a2a7c","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc1bf9e595a0898ae9b98224d3bc53f2e8debf3","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"身邊有啲人六月中仲係傻豬豬乜都唔知<br />\n到而家會係fb ig到出post屌膠官<br />\n覺得已經係進步<br />\n<br />\n可能我要求太低<br />\n咁樣就滿足<br />\n不過都要接受下唔係個個都係鄺仔<br />\n可以一下子由1.0變4.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 同目標嘅 各有各做啦<br />\n比啲時間大家進化"},{"pid":"3894fd686e8fa59aeb59c27c412574dba6bc52b5","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f4c113cb5807b1af7e78900ba64f18c416ab948","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d7551754d