.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 同目標嘅 各有各做啦<br />\n比啲時間大家進化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"其實今次有好多淺藍至中立變成淺黃至深黃<br />\n當然遠遠唔夠，五大訴求其實一項都未做到<br />\n但係互屌只會連呢少少成就都破壞埋<br />\n今場仗好可能係一場以年做單位嘅硬仗<br />\n大家要互相扶持，不互屌不分化，先有機會增加贏面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab14831cc250b9c1e1ba2ee779f51afc0c862c3","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b565a0e23cfc6c825be5192ceef183475e81050a","tid":1394741,"uid":193251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"已灰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"咁就休息下，休息係為左行更遠嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554f0eea759d7362016bba7c6cf13cbe1350383d","tid":1394741,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28da9faa062fd2ef3b9dda6bce5a16cbc9747097","tid":1394741,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d261088fd9472c769acc0c9317bd70e3d2537ce","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b565a0e23cfc6c825be5192ceef183475e81050a","tid":1394741,"uid":193251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"已灰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"抖一抖好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a675f969dabc078c9225823e0c079225bbea4770","tid":1394741,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家坐埋同一條船 洗濕左個頭"},{"pid":"481efd86a23530