:{"pid":"6f1b294a75665acf396bbc90208bada829f6043e","tid":1394741,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7670ef6e999932e1a32173b446911e0751a896e6","tid":1394741,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69392cebee69ba2da01ef6d6fad42cd1ae283ff","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6f1b294a75665acf396bbc90208bada829f6043e","tid":1394741,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"記住量力而為<br />\n有勇都要有謀，唔係勇字當頭就死衝，記住be water<br />\n體能唔夠好就做啲自己handle 到嘅嘢<br />\n我四年無做過運動，都係呢排開始練返體能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07fe46f4f31367d1cf49b127b74e606dcaa5cf9","tid":1394741,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:27:26.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"0090f4ee1cd2ab0946eb6fec18ce109387f32dff","tid":1394741,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7670ef6e999932e1a32173b446911e0751a896e6","tid":1394741,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1658a154bcc77e8b08bc9e33a8f608160bcfb42d","tid":1394741,"uid":265622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"義士們加油！<br />\n雖然連番日子的抗爭都未有辦法迫使政府讓，令大家一直諗著我地無嬴到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請記住我地到e加都無輸到！只要未認輸就仲有得翻盤！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe water<br />\n冷靜尋找勝機"},{"pid":"ad2eade69ce1c445f07d5aef9e04a217b7e5fa8b","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7670ef6e999932e1a32173b446911e0751a896e6","tid":1394741,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"我有朋友次次奮戰到最後一刻<br />\n自己要照顧三個老人家去唔到上前線，只可以做和理非<br />\n我朋友好在無俾人ban，但係我每晚合埋眼都好恨自己無同佢地一齊戰鬥<br />\n呢種感覺我真係明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有曬馬已經好撚有勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係你依家身體支撐唔到，你就要退落黎休息，無人會怪你<br />\n休息係為左行更遠嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係身體休息嘅同時，如果心理質素okay 嘅不妨轉職做文宣，做和理非，加入不合作運動e.g. 搭地鐵/update 連儂牆/去新城市灑溪錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337e92c1cd7bca5e5a2201d712e99dd3733d1057","tid":1394741,"uid":285118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"間唔中仲見到有人屌人咩淨係出ig post屌正苦屌狗係無用<br />\n講真po下文宣屌下狗發洩都係spread資訊嘅一種方法姐<br />\n<br />\n所以真係各有各做 每個人都有唔同方法努力去做<br />\n唔好覺得人地做得少"},{"pid":"c6245d7758e4495cab3cdad66d6229f77b77435a","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1658a154bcc77e8b08bc9e33a8f608160bcfb42d","tid":1394741,"uid":265622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"義士們加油！<br />\n雖然連番日子的抗爭都未有辦法迫使政府讓，令大家一直諗著我地無嬴到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請記住我地到e加都無輸到！只要未認輸就仲有得翻盤！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe water<br />\n冷靜尋找勝機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n有賭未為輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9976ac80c84e7a4181e031ed0c88e718ffbb7bd","tid":1394741,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228924e49409f079b63208c103b8b5b14ccc7008","tid":1394741,"uid":179738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"自己體弱發夢上前線好似會拖累大隊 覺得自己好廢 發夢係現場行行企企成舊垃圾咁完全唔知做乜鳩 好想真係衝出去比人拉或者比狗打死算 再加上屋企人深藍好反對我發夢 同屋企人關係極差 次次都要偷出去 日日都係到屌鳩我 每個星期六日都話班手足開始搞事 叫我即刻返去 我唔理唔聽佢地電話就係咁打電話黎屌鳩我同講班手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好嬲好想離開呢個屋企 身邊除左老豆老母之外 好多人都支持發夢 點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經放棄左自己 夢就一定要發 要拉要死我完全唔介意"},{"pid":"e86d2964f932eb2e3072ab705c8ac183526643b7","tid":1394741,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ab14831cc250b9c1e1ba2ee779f51afc0c862c3","tid":1394741,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b565a0e23cfc6c825be5192ceef183475e81050a","tid":1394741,"uid":193251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"已灰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"咁就休息下，休息係為左行更遠嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"倒不如&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin